 Plot Synopsis                                                                                  

A release that caters to the innumerable fans of French-Canadian soft rock diva   Celine Dion, the performance package Celine Dion: A New Day - Live in Las Vegas pays homage to Dion&#039;s stunning 5-year run at Caesar&#039;s Palace in Las Vegas, Nevada, where her show &#039;A New Day(created in tandem with Belgian film and stage director Franco Dragone) drew a massive 3,000,000 attendees. Celine Dion: A New Day - Live in Las Vegas incorporates a 93 minute concert film edited together from several of the Vegas performances, plus a video tribute to Celine&#039;s fans entitled &#039;Because You Loved Me,&#039; and two additional bonus documentaries,&#039;A New Day: The Secrets&#039; and &#039;A %New Day: All Access,&#039; which carry viewers on a behind-the-scenes tour of    the seminal show. ~ Nathan Southern, All Movie Guide
